actions.text: Introduced in the Senate. Read twice. Placed on Senate Legislative Calendar under General Orders. Calendar No. 624.

official_title: A bill to nullify the Supplemental Treaty Between the United States of America and the Confederated Tribes and Bands of Indians of Middle Oregon, concluded on November 15, 1865.

summary.text: Nullifies the Supplemental Treaty Between the United States of America and the Confederated Tribe and Bands of Indians of Middle Oregon, concluded on November 15, 1865.
